beer.beer_description: Brew ‘A’ IPA has a level of hop addition (Enigma and Cascade) to achieve high bitterness and fruit flavours of melon, berry, stone fruit and citrus. The pale and crystal malts used in this brew give a malty biscuit aftertaste. Only 1500 kegs have been released across Australia. Find a tap near you and enjoy this beer before it's gone!
